'''Radio Mashaal''' ({{lang-ps|مشال راډیو}}) is a member of [[Radio Free Europe]] in [[Pakistan]].<ref name="rfe">[http://www.rferl.org/section/Pakistan/1074.html Radio Mashaal overview]</ref> It was launched in January 2010.<ref name="rfe"/><ref name="bbg">[http://www.bbg.gov/pressroom/press-releases/RFE_Marks_Successful_First_Year_of_Broadcasts_to_Pakistan_.html Broadcasting Board of Governors]</ref> It broadcasts in the [[Pashto language]].<ref name="rfe"/><ref name="bbg"/> Its headquarters are both in [[Prague]], [[Czech Republic]], and in [[Islamabad]], [[Pakistan]].<ref name="rfe"/>

